# Build context for agents/orchestrator/Dockerfile is the repo root, but the image
# only needs the agents package + pyproject + README. Whitelist those and exclude
# everything else — critically web/node_modules (symlinks break asset staging on
# Windows) and the virtualenvs / VCS / caches.
*
!agents
!pyproject.toml
!README.md

# Re-exclude noise inside the whitelisted agents tree.
agents/**/__pycache__
agents/**/*.pyc
agents/**/.pytest_cache
agents/**/tests
